            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Instead of passing `NULL` when the default format is not being used and the default format otherwise. Why not just always pass the statusline string that will be used (user-configured statusline string if it exists and default statusline string otherwise) instead of letting `redraw_custom_statusline` choose the statusline string when `NULL` is passed?\r\n\r\n",
